e five loaves for the five thousand and how many baskets you collected? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Or the seven loaves for the four thousand and how many large baskets you collected?"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 14:17–21","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 15:34–38","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":34,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 14:17–21","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":17},{"label":"Mt 15:34–38","book":"Mat","chapter":15,"verse":34}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Why is it you don’t understand that when I told you, ‘Beware of the leaven of the Pharisees and Sadducees,’ it wasn’t about bread?”"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 3:7","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:6","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:1","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 3:7","book":"Mat","chapter":3,"verse":7},{"label":"Mt 16:6","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":6},{"label":"Mk 8:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":15},{"label":"Lk 12:1","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then they understood that he had not told them to beware of the leaven in bread, but of the teaching of the Pharisees and Sadducees. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:20","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":20,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 17:13","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 23:3","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":3,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 5:20","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":20},{"label":"Mt 17:13","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":13},{"label":"Mt 23:3","book":"Mat","chapter":23,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"When Jesus came to the region of Caesarea Philippi, "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"A town north of Galilee at the base of Mount Hermon"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 8:27–29","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":27,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:18–20","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" he asked his disciples, “Who do people say that the Son of Man is?”"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read that I, the Son of Man, am"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 8:27–29","book":"Mrk","chapter":8,"verse":27},{"label":"Lk 9:18–20","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":18}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"A town north of Galilee at the base of Mount Hermon"},{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read that I, the Son of Man, am"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"They replied, “Some say John the Baptist; others, Elijah; still others, Jeremiah or one of the prophets.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 14:2","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 17:10","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 6:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 9:8","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:21","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":21,"letter":"e"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 14:2","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":2},{"label":"Mt 17:10","book":"Mat","chapter":17,"verse":10},{"label":"Mk 6:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":6,"verse":15},{"label":"Lk 9:8","book":"Luk","chapter":9,"verse":8},{"label":"Jn 1:21","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“But you,” he asked them, “who do you say that I am?”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Simon Peter answered, “You are the Messiah, the Son of the living God.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 1:16","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 11:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":27,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 1:16","book":"Mat","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Jn 11:27","book":"Jhn","chapter":11,"verse":27}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Jesus responded, “Blessed are you, Simon son of Jonah,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or son of John"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 1:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":42,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 21:15–17","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" because flesh and blood did not reveal this to you, but my Father in heaven."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 15:50","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":50,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 6:12","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":12,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 2:14","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":14,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jn 1:42","book":"Jhn","chapter":1,"verse":42},{"label":"Jn 21:15–17","book":"Jhn","chapter":21,"verse":15},{"label":"1Co 15:50","book":"1Co","chapter":15,"verse":50},{"label":"Gl 1:16","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":16},{"label":"Eph 6:12","book":"Eph","chapter":6,"verse":12},{"label":"Heb 2:14","book":"Heb","chapter":2,"verse":14}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or son of John"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And I also say to you that you are Peter, and on this rock I will build my church,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:17","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 5:11","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":11,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 7:38","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":38,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 8:3","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":3,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 9:31","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":31,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 11:22","book":"Act","chapter":11,"verse":22,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 11:26","book":"Act","chapter":11,"verse":26,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"text","text":" and the gates of Hades will not overpower it. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 18:17","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":17},{"label":"Ac 5:11","book":"Act","chapter":5,"verse":11},{"label":"Ac 7:38","book":"Act","chapter":7,"verse":38},{"label":"Ac 8:1","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":1},{"label":"Ac 8:3","book":"Act","chapter":8,"verse":3},{"label":"Ac 9:31","book":"Act","chapter":9,"verse":31},{"label":"Ac 11:22","book":"Act","chapter":11,"verse":22},{"label":"Ac 11:26","book":"Act","chapter":11,"verse":26}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:16:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"I will give you the keys of the kingdom of heaven,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 22:22","book":"Isa","chapter":22,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:18","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 20:23","book":"Jhn","chapter":20,"verse":23,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 1:18","book":"Rev","chapter":1,"verse":18,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Rv 3:7","book":"Rev","chapter":3,"verse":7,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"text","text":" and whatever you bind on earth will have been bound"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Or earth will be bound"},{"kind":"text","text":" in heaven, and whatever 